title: Redfish Power Subsystem
agents: agent_redfish
catalog: hw/server/redfish
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the power subsystem of Redfish devices that use
 the newer Sensor resource model. It reports total PSU capacity,
 power allocation, and power supply redundancy status.

discovery:
 One service is created for each chassis power subsystem.

item:
